     I                                        5   60WSSSSS
     I                                        7  100WSSYYY
     I                                       11  120WSSMMM
     I                                       13  140WSSDDD
     I                                        1   40WSSTM4
     I                                        1   60WSSTM6
     I                                        7  140WSSDAT
     I* USER PART
