TCHK2C                     KFLD           Q5NKOJ
TCHK2C                     KFLD           Q5NUKE
TCHK2C                     KFLD           Q5MHN1
TCHK2C                     KFLD           Q5MHN2
TCHK2C                     KFLD           Q5MHN3
